_source.title: Sample Decisions Shipment - Help
_source.visState:
{"title":"Sample Decisions Shipment - Help","type":"markdown","params":{"fontSize":12,"markdown":"### Sample Decisions Shipment dashboard

This dashboard displays data from running the Shipment Pricing decision service model. The dashboard is divided into the following sections:
1. Global 
* Sample Decisions Shipment - Help: This page describes the different sections in the dashboard.
* Sample Decisions Shipment - Request and average price: This section shows the number of shipment pricing requests and the average price of the requests.
* Sample Decisions Shipment - Data distribution: This pie chart displays information about the shipment pricing requests:
  - Size of shipments
  - Weight of shipments
  - Transportation mode for shipments

2. Analysis of the price 
* Sample Decisions Shipment - Requests per price (distance): This section shows the number of shipment requests stacked by distance in price intervals of $5.
* Sample Decisions Shipment - Requests per price (size): This section shows the number of shipment requests stacked by size in price intervals of $5.
* Sample Decisions Shipment - Average price per size (transportation mode): This section shows the average price per size stacked by transportation mode.
* Sample Decisions Shipment - Average price per distance (transportation mode): This section shows the average price per distance stacked by transportation mode.
* Sample Decisions Shipment - Requests per price (customer loyalty): This section shows the number of shipment requests by customer loyalty in price intervals of $5.
* Sample Decisions Shipment - Requests per delivery (size): This section shows the number of shipment requests for a delivery stacked by size.
3. Sample Decisions Shipment - Executed rules: This section shows the fired rules and the number of times each rule has been fired.
4. Sample Decisions Shipment - Search

All the widgets are set to filter on the ShipmentPricing ruleset. All the widgets are prefixed with Sample Decisions Shipment to make them easier to find.
Note that all the charts use the horizontal grid display.
For more information, see the  [Business Automation Insights documentation](https://www.ibm.com/support/knowledgecenter/SSYHZ8_18.0.x/com.ibm.dba.bai/topics/con_bai_dashboards.html).","openLinksInNewTab":false},"aggs":[]}
